er to provide a clear description of\nthe optical absorption spectra, we use group theory to derive the optical\nselection rules between LDS for both $\\chi_{\\parallel}$ and $\\chi_{\\perp}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2017 21:15:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-05"}
