g ekpyrotic\nequilibrium point undergoes the phenomenon of anisotropic inflation if\n$-3\\Lambda/5 < V_0 < 0$, where $\\Lambda > 0$ is the cosmological constant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2017 21:33:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-10"}
