he Taylor\ndiffusion associated with a vector field where the heat operator $L_{t}$\nappears naturally.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2017 10:32:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 May 2017 10:32:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Jan 2018 14:05:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-24"}
